data.description: Lake Riverside Ranch/Farmhouse offers 2024SF of living space on 2.65 fully level and fenced/cross fenced acres with mature trees, stables, and outbuildings! Auto gate entry leads to your beautiful ranch home with so many great features to offer! Interior downstairs cabin style knotty pine wood walls, formal spacious living space, downstairs powder room, kitchen open for family/dining room with wet bar and LOTS of storage!!!! Enjoy the spacious covered raised deck in your private backyard which is cross fenced for privacy. Upstairs you will find a full bath with 3 bedrooms. The primary bedroom has a recently renovated bathroom with new flooring, vanity, and lighting. The home itself has had many upgrades in the past 10 years to include a new roof in 2014, upgraded dual pane windows which open up or down, tankless water heater, and replaced well pump. Recently the HVAC had been upgraded and a whole house Generac system installed. The ranch portion of the property is adorably charming with custom built pens with weather safe stables and custom raised cover structures perfect for little goats or chickens. In addition to the attached 2 car garage there is a detached 2 car garage, a workshop building and exterior new condition custom installed TuffSheds on concrete! A private well offers zero water bill and will be certified during escrow. This home is not far from the main community gate but far enough from the highway. Miles of riding trails right outside the gate! Lake Riverside is a historic equestrian and aviation community offering a 55 acre fishing lake, tot lot, sports courts, meeting room, pool, bbq areas, 3600 lighted airstrip and equestrian center with arena, roundpen and stalls. Cal Fire resides right within the community! A must see gem priced just right!
